        {
            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "<img width=\"2520\" height=\"1176\" alt=\"Image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/1c97f26c-364d-416a-b1b3-b4b93163e4d0\" />\n\nhmm for me it works ( `git difftool 62dcd07787 runtime/pack/dist/opt/netrw/doc/netrw.txt` )\n\nwith -d `git difftool 62dcd07787 runtime/pack/dist/opt/netrw/doc/netrw.txt -d`\n\n<img width=\"2533\" height=\"1214\" alt=\"Image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/8584c8c6-098a-48ff-bd98-15676d4c4ea1\" />\n\nWith config like this\n\n```\n[diff]\n    algorithm = histogram\n    colorMoved = true\n    colorMovedWS = allow-indentation-change\n    mnemonicPrefix = true\n\n    tool = nvim_difftool\n    submodule = diff\n\n[difftool]\n    prompt = true\n    trustExitCode = true\n\n[difftool \"nvim_difftool\"]\n    cmd = nvim -c \\\"packadd nvim.difftool\\\" -d \\\"$LOCAL\\\" \\\"$REMOTE\\\"\n```",
            "created_at": "2026-05-20T08:30:27Z",
